OL,3,CAsylum seekers to be moved to military
OL,4,Csites in bid to reduce hotel use
OL,6,FHundreds of asylum seekers will be
OL,7,Fmoved to military sites, as the
OL,8,Fgovernment pledges to "close every
OL,9,Fasylum hotel" used to house migrants.
OL,11,FThe Home Office has confirmed that two
OL,12,Fbarracks in Scotland and southern
OL,13,FEngland would be used to house around
OL,14,F900 men temporarily, with officials
OL,15,Fworking to identify more sites in the
OL,16,Fcoming weeks and months.
OL,18,FThe plans will see men housed at
OL,19,FCameron Barracks in Inverness and
OL,20,FCrowborough Training Camp in East
OL,21,FSussex.
