OL,3,CAsylum seekers to be moved to military
OL,4,Csites in bid to reduce hotel use
OL,6,FBoth sites were used accommodate
OL,7,FAfghan families evacuated during the
OL,8,Fwithdrawal from Kabul in 2021.
OL,10,FIt comes after a committee of MPs
OL,11,Faccused the Home Office of wasting
OL,12,Fbillions of pounds on hotels housing
OL,13,Fasylum seekers, in what it called a
OL,14,F"failed, chaotic and expensive" system.
OL,16,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,17,Fare furious at the level of illegal
OL,18,Fmigrants and asylum hotels.
