OL,6,F"This government will close every
OL,7,Fasylum hotel. Work is well under way,
OL,8,Fwith more suitable sites being brought
OL,9,Fforward to ease pressure on
OL,10,Fcommunities and cut asylum costs."
OL,12,FOther options being considered include
OL,13,Fmilitary and industrial sites,
OL,14,Ftemporary facilities and disused
OL,15,Faccommodation, and officials have been
OL,16,Fordered to accelerate work identifying
OL,17,Falternatives.
