OL,6,FExpected costs of Home Office
OL,7,Faccommodation contracts for 2019-2029
OL,8,Fhave tripled from #4.5 billion to
OL,9,F#15.3 billion, following what the
OL,10,FCommons Home Affairs Committee called
OL,11,Fa "dramatic increase" in demand.
OL,13,FOn Monday, Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,14,FStarmer said he was "frustrated and
OL,15,Fangry" as he sought to blame the
OL,16,Fprevious government for leaving a
OL,17,F"huge mess" in the asylum system by
OL,18,Ffailing to process people's claims.
